Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:56.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What? They rushed off of the island? - OG}O quê? Eles saíram correndo da ilha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim. Não conseguimos nem\Ndar o presente a eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.47,0:02:01.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How disappointing... - OG}Que pena...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.98,0:02:07.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if they even realize how\Nmuch we appreciate what they did. - OG}Será que eles sequer percebem\No quão gratos somos pelo que fizeram.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.32,0:02:13.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Exactly. They have no idea how I feel. - OG}De fato. Eles ainda não\Nentendem nossos sentimentos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:18.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não é justo, Aisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:20.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that you alone\Ngot to say goodbye to them. - OG}Você foi a única que conseguiu\Nse despedir deles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:24.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Everyone's in an uproar that\Nwe let our saviors run away. - OG}Eles não param de falar sobre\Ncomo deixamos nossos salvadores fugirem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:29.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas Luffy e os outros\Nme pediram pra não contar a ninguém.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.34,0:02:34.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey Raki, did you know?\NLuffy's body stretches! - OG}Ei Raki, sabia que o\Ncorpo do Luffy estica?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:37.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele fazia tipo, "Gum-Gum Pistol!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:40.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, Aisa, don't move! - OG}Ei, Aisa, fica quieta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:43.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I didn't know there was a strong\Nwarrior like him in the Blue Sea, too. - OG}Quem diria que tinha um guerreiro\Nforte no Blue Sea também?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:48.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quero ser como ele,\Ntipo "Gum-Gum...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:51.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:56.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's just trim your hair for\Ntoday. Let your hair grow. - OG}Vamos só aparar um pouco hoje.\NVocê devia deixar o cabelo crescer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:01.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que vai ficar bonito.\NVocê é menina, tem que ficar fofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:06.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fofa?! Eu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:08.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right... - OG}Isso mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:12.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{since there won't be any need\Nfor you kids to carry arms... - OG}Agora que não tem mais necessidade\Nde vocês crianças carregarem armas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:19.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and since you can now live freely,\Nlike people in the sky should. - OG}vocês podem viver livres,\Ncomo as pessoas no céu deveriam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.14,0:03:23.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're ladylike today. - OG}Você está bem feminina hoje!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, don't move, Aisa! - OG}Agora, fica quieta, Aisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Raki feminina!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:29.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:38.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Grande Guerreiro Kalgara...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.87,0:03:43.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We were told that the Shandians'\Nrole had been fulfilled. - OG}Fomos informados de que o dever sagrado\Ndos Shandianos foi cumprido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:47.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And I'm sure your wish was\Ndelivered to your best friend as well. - OG}E tenho certeza de que seu melhor amigo\Ntambém ouviu seu desejo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:53.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We no longer have to make\Nfuture generations shed blood. - OG}As gerações futuras não precisarão\Nmais derramar seu sangue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:59.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The battle is over...\Nbut we won't lose our pride! - OG}Nossa luta pode ter acabado...\Nmas nunca perderemos nosso orgulho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.59,0:04:03.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então por favor continue a velar por nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.31,0:04:09.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We swear that we will not let the\Nfire of Shandia go out ever again! - OG}Juramos manter a Luz de Shandora\Nbrilhando para sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.24,0:04:23.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I am the Sky Knight,\Na freelance soldier-for-hire. - OG}Eu sou apenas o Sky Knight,\Num mercenário freelancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:26.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're the best suited for it. - OG}Você é muito mais adequado pra isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esta cidade pertencia ao seu\Npovo desde o início.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:31.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's this all of a sudden? - OG}O que é isso agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse não é um bom motivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:36.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{With this battle, I think\Neveryone must have realized... - OG}Acho que esta batalha\Nnos ensinou a dura verdade...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:40.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{that no one can own Vearth. - OG}de que ninguém pode reivindicar\Na posse de vearth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{"God" is our support. - OG}O título de "deus" dá força.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:47.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O nome da terra é Skypiea.\NO nome da cidade é Shandora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A única pessoa que\Npode unificá-las é você,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:55.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{who continued to be anguished\Nby the battle in this land. - OG}aquele que sempre sofreu com\Na guerra interminável desta terra.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:59.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sky Knight Gan Fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:01.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I would like\Nyou to take the seat of God again, - OG}Eu peço que assuma o posto de deus novamente
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.57,0:05:05.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and support this land\Nwhose scar is still deep. - OG}e dê a esta nação ferida\Na força para se curar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:09.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós também gostaríamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gan Fall-sama!- OG}Senhor Gan Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:12.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If it's you, we'll accept it, too! - OG}Se for você,\Nnós apoiamos também!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Gan Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:16.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please come back! - OG}Precisamos de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Honestly... - OG}Puxa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:28.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Just when I thought I could finally\Nreally enjoy growing pumpkins... - OG}Justo quando pensei que finalmente\Npoderia cultivar abóboras em paz...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.63,0:05:57.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal! Já dá pra ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:06:01.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please look to the\Nfront! It's Cloud End! - OG}Olhem lá na frente! É o Cloud End!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ah! Let's see! - OG}Ah! Deixa eu ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I see... So we can go\Nback down from there? - OG}Uau... Então podemos descer\Npor ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chegamos mais cedo do que eu pensava.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.27,0:06:13.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So we're going back down, huh? - OG}Já temos que ir embora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:17.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, now that we're about to\Ngo back, I admit I hate to leave. - OG}É, agora que estamos voltando,\Nnão quero me despedir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's time to say goodbye\Nto this pure white sea. - OG}Está na hora de dar adeus\Na este mar branco e puro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:23.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The sky island was fun...\Nthough it was scary. - OG}A ilha do céu foi divertida...\Nmas também foi assustadora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:28.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So once we go through that gate,\Nwe'll be heading straight down - OG}{to the Blue Sea via\Na Milky Road, huh? - OG}{\q2}Então tem uma estrada láctea ali que\Ndesce direto pro Blue Sea, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if we can visit\Nthe sky island again... - OG}Será que vamos visitar\Na ilha do céu de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hard to tell with this place. - OG}Talvez sim, talvez não.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:47.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well then, everyone! I'm sorry! We'll say goodbye here! - OG}Bom, pessoal! Desculpem,\Nmas vamos nos despedir aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se cuidem, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:51.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por nos despedirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Conis! Se cuide!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say hello to the others! - OG}Mande um abraço pros outros também!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:58.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado por tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:07.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, we should be thanking you! - OG}Não! Nós é que devemos agradecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nunca vou esquecer vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Conis, old guy and little\Nwhite one! You all take care! - OG}Conis, velhote e bolinha de pelo!\NSe cuidem todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes! - OG}– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:19.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora, recolham as velas imediatamente\Ne segurem firme no navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:21.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Alright! Do as the old guy said! - OG}Certo! Vamos fazer o que ele disse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:23.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que vai ser bem rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:27.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, we're sliding from a 7,000-meter height! Hurry up! - OG}É, vamos deslizar 7.000\Nmetros! Andem!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Ok!\N– Ok!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?! What?! - OG}Q-Quê?! Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:40.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele diz, "Não esqueçam de mim."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:43.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Oh... That's the South Bird we\Nbrought to the sky with us. - OG}Ah... É aquele pássaro do sul que\Ntrouxemos pro céu com a gente.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:48.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, Captain! - OG}Ok, Capitão!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:51.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Conseguimos o log pra próxima ilha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:59.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Once we get off from here,\Nwe'll start on a new adventure again! - OG}Certo! Quando descermos,\Nvamos começar uma aventura nova!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Guys! You ready?! - OG}Estão prontos, pessoal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.67,0:08:07.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/fad(150,0)]We're gonna go back to the Blue Sea! - OG}{\fad(150,0)}Estamos voltando pro Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:25.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal! Cuidado na descida!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{While dropping? - OG}– Descida?\N– Descida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:50.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here we go! The sky island's\Nfamous Octopus Balloon! - OG}Lá vamos nós! O famoso\Noctobalão da ilha do céu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:04.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's an octopus! - OG}Um polvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu filho da...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:11.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ow-ow... - OG}A-Ai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Wh-What?! What the...?! - OG}Q-Q-Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:18.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, olha! Que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabos é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.75,0:09:24.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É um balão!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:26.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso é divertido!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:27.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desaceleramos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:32.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu... Achei que finalmente\Nia pro outro mundo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:06.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Ring it! See off the saviors of\Nthis land by ringing the bell! - OG}Toquem! Deixem o sino\Ndespedir-se dos salvadores desta terra!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.17,0:10:07.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Heso!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:13.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Luffy! See you again! - OG}Luffy! Vamos nos ver de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:14.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Come visit us again! - OG}Não some não!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.80,0:10:16.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:20.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Go back to the Blue Sea safely! - OG}Boa viagem de volta ao Blue Sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.61,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{When you look up, you see the sky. - OG}Quando você olha\Npara o céu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:34.66,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{Is this God's Land on the\Nclouds a dream or reality? - OG}É real, ou é apenas um sonho,\Nesta Terra de Deus acima das nuvens?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.45,0:10:37.45,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{10,000 meters far up in the sky... - OG}Dez mil metros acima no céu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:41.04,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you listen carefully, you\Ncan hear the sound of the bell. - OG}Se ouvir com atenção, pode\Nouvir o som de um sino.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:43.96,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{It rings today, and it will\Nring again tomorrow. - OG}Ele toca hoje. E vai\Ntocar novamente amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:47.29,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{The sound of the bell\Nthat echoes in the sky - OG}O som ecoante\Ndo sino no céu
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:51.76,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,{glorifies and sings about\Nthe wandering land... - OG}canta o triunfo desta\Nterra errante...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:02.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:06.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! This feels so good! - OG}É! Isso é demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai cancelar a busca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's just natural, right?! The\Ncity of gold was in the sky. - OG}É só natural, né?!\NA Cidade do Ouro estava no céu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:18.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não vamos encontrar nada\Nno fundo do mar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.16,0:11:20.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Este é o fim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tem sentido ficar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Old-timer... - OG}Chefe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Old-timer... - OG}Chefe...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.17,0:11:33.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I really thank you all... for joining\Nme to pursue my dream for years. - OG}{\q2}Agradeço sinceramente a todos vocês... por me\Nacompanharem na busca do meu sonho todos esses anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.84,0:11:35.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What're you saying...? - OG}O que está dizendo...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:37.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não nos trate como estranhos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Say, you guys! - OG}Então, senhores!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.89,0:11:44.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What kind of romanticism\Nshall we go after next?! - OG}Que tipo de aventura romântica\Nvamos perseguir agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.90,0:11:54.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll follow you to the ends\Nof the earth, old-timer! - OG}Vamos seguir você até os confins\Ndo mundo, chefe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:03.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ouro! Ouro! Ouro! Ouro! Ouro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.79,0:12:07.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We've finally become super rich! What shall we buy?! - OG}Finalmente somos super ricos!\NO que vamos comprar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:11.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How about buying a huge bronze statue?! - OG}Que tal uma estátua de bronze enorme?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You moron! What's the point of\Nexchanging gold with bronze?! - OG}Seu idiota! Por que trocaria\Nouro por bronze?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.59,0:12:16.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We should increase the\Nnumber of cannons! - OG}Devíamos comprar canhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:18.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos comprar dez! Dez!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:21.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Nami-san! I want a\Nlockable refrigerator! - OG}Nami! Eu quero\Numa geladeira com cadeado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:25.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não seja idiota! O que vamos\Nfazer quando der fome?! Protesto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:25.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu... Eu... Quero que\Ncomprem livros pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's just why we should\Nbuy it, you dumb ass! - OG}É justamente por isso que devemos\Ncomprar, imbecil!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{[/an8]I want to read medical\Nbooks from other countries! - OG}{\an8}Quero ler livros de medicina\Nde outros países!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey, hold on a second, you guys! - OG}Ei, esperem um segundo, pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:34.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos dividir o tesouro quando\Ndescermos, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, comprem livros pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.57,0:12:40.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we buy whatever you guys like, I have a feeling that it won't do us any good. - OG}Se gastarmos nosso dinheiro de qualquer jeito,\Nvamos acabar desperdiçando tudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:52.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O sol já se pôs completamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But it's a nice view. - OG}Mas a vista é bonita.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É, você tem razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's cold...! - OG}Tá congelando...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:13.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami! Robin! Vocês estão bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.07,0:13:18.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que susto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The octopus\Nsuddenly shrunk all the way! - OG}O polvo de repente\Nencolheu totalmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.16,0:13:22.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if the air leaked out. - OG}Talvez tenha sido um vazamento de ar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:30.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But we somehow made\Nit down... without dying. - OG}Bom, de algum jeito conseguimos\Ndescer... sem morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:32.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You! Thanks! - OG}Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:33.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ainda assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:41.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nós realmente fomos a um\Nlugar incrível, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:44.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now that we've fallen, it's so far up. - OG}Agora que estamos aqui embaixo,\Nparece tão distante.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:46.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's as if we were dreaming. - OG}É como se estivéssemos sonhando.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:49.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É uma terra de sonhos. Será que\Na gente pode visitar de novo um dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.31,0:13:52.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Talvez você consiga\Nchegar mais perto se morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:55.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Zoro, so you think you\Ncan go to heaven? - OG}Zoro, você realmente acha\Nque vai ser aceito no céu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:57.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You jerk! - OG}Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:00.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Well, things're calm now at any rate. - OG}De qualquer forma, as coisas se acalmaram.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou fazer um café ou algo assim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.86,0:14:03.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'd rather have dinner, Sanji! - OG}Melhor ainda, faz\Num jantar pra gente, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:07.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm saying I'll get on it right away,\Nso have some coffee and wait! - OG}É, é, já vou fazer.\NFiquem aí e tomem um café.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:13.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And given all that gold, we'd each\Nhave gotten so much money! - OG}É saque pirata,\Nentão vamos dividir igualmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:16.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Divided up?! - OG}Cada um ganha uma parte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:16.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Naturalmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estava esperando por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:21.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm\Ngonna buy me a bronze statue! - OG}Vou comprar uma estátua de bronze!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.01,0:14:22.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Can we buy books?! I\Nwant the latest medical books! - OG}É! Posso comprar livros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:28.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{New pots and frying pans, plus\Nsilverware and giant mousetraps... - OG}Panelas novas, frigideiras, talheres\Ne ratoeiras gigantes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.06,0:14:30.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ainda sobra um monte!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:32.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Posso beber o quanto quiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:35.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{First, my stash will be 80%! - OG}Primeiro, 80 por cento vai pro meu caixa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hold on a second! - OG}– Espera aí!\N– Espera aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Brincadeira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:43.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Obviously! You can't just\Nopenly have a secret stash! - OG}Óbvio! Não se pode ter\Num cofre secreto público!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:49.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{By "stash," I mean money\Nsaved up to repair the ship! - OG}Por "caixa" eu quero dizer\No fundo de reparo do navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:52.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ship? You mean Merry? - OG}O navio? Quer dizer o Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:56.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's right. The Going Merry is\Nwhat brought us where we are now. - OG}Isso mesmo. O Going Merry é\No que nos trouxe até aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pensando bem,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.84,0:15:04.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{it has given us a ride on the seas\Never since my East Blue village... - OG}{\q2}ela é nosso transporte pelos mares\Ndesde minha vila no East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.01,0:15:07.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's done so much for us,\Nbut now it's all beat up. - OG}Ela fez tanto por nós,\Nmas agora está toda arrebentada.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:10.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Boa ideia! A Grande Reforma\Ndo Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.89,0:15:12.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tô dentro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dig in. - OG}Certo, podem comer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:19.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Usopp's cheap repairs\Nare just about at their limit. - OG}{\q2}É, pensando bem, os reparos\Nbaratos do Usopp estão no limite.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:22.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll have you know that I'm a sniper! - OG}Ei, eu sou só atirador, tá!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:28.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Yeah. We should go to\Na real shipbuilding dock and have real shipwrights fix it for us. - OG}É. Devíamos ir a um estaleiro de verdade\Ne ter carpinteiros navais de verdade pra consertar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{There are people better than\Nyou at fixing ships, Usopp? - OG}Tem gente que conserta navios\Nmelhor que o Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sometimes you gotta\Ntake extra good care, - OG}Temos que consertá-la direitinho\Nde vez em quando,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.04,0:15:36.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{or you'll wind up paying for it later! - OG}ou vamos nos arrepender depois!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right, it's decided! - OG}Certo, está decidido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's get a shipwright in our crew! - OG}Vamos adicionar um carpinteiro naval à tripulação!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Our journey is far from over! - OG}Ainda temos um longo caminho pela frente!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes! - OG}– É!\N– É!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.47,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We need those skills anyway... - OG}Precisamos de alguém\Ncom essas habilidades de qualquer forma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:49.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{And Merry is our home! - OG}{\i1}O Merry é nosso lar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.35,0:15:51.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nossa vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:55.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's find a shipwright\Nwho can keep it safe! - OG}Vamos encontrar um carpinteiro naval\Nque possa mantê-la a salvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.90,0:15:59.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Lá vai ele de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:03.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, on rare occasion,\Nhe gets straight to the point. - OG}É, de vez em quando\Nele acerta em cheio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:06.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's the best way! Let's do it! - OG}Seria perfeito! Vamos fazer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ok, então esse é o plano!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:10.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espero que encontremos alguém bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E precisamos de um músico também!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No, just forget about that. - OG}Não, não precisamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's all the ruckus here?! - OG}Qual é todo esse barulho?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.34,0:16:23.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Corram!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:27.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de empurrar! T-Temos que\Nficar longe deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{They're having a falling out?! - OG}Uma briga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sarquiss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:45.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor! Faça ele parar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:51.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Please! Stop! Why\Nare you doing this...?! - OG}Por favor! Para com isso!\NPor que está fazendo isso...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:53.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:55.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Sarquiss is in pain! - OG}Sarquiss é quem está implorando pra parar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.33,0:16:59.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por quê? Você pergunta por quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:02.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sarquiss... Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's because you've tarnished\Nthis symbol of mine, of course. - OG}É porque você desrespeitou\Na minha bandeira, é claro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"A ilha do céu existe ou não?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:17.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,"A Cidade do Ouro é real ou não?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:22.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't give a care about any of that. - OG}Eu não poderia me importar menos com isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're to twist people around by\Ntaking advantage of differing opinions. - OG}"Coloque crença contra crença\Npara obter controle sobre os outros."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Foi o que eu te disse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,não foi, Bellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:35.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é... Donquixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:38.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele é um dos Sete\NGuerreiros do Mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He used to have a\Nbounty over 300 million! - OG}A recompensa dele era\Nde mais de 300 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que um cara como ele está fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:47.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu não preciso de inúteis\Ncomo vocês me servindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:51.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Meu corpo está se movendo sozinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:54.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para! Por favor, não...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:56.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:08.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Me dê...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:11.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me dê mais uma chance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:16.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I–we– will follow you loyally! - OG}Eu... Nós seremos seus seguidores leais!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:19.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chega, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:25.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu perdi, mas nunca fui\Ncontra seus princípios!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I swear on your symbol! - OG}Eu juro pela sua bandeira!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:29.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse é o meu jeito de fazer as coisas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We couldn't just run 'im off; - OG}Não podíamos simplesmente expulsá-lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:35.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{he would've reached you someday! - OG}Ele teria chegado até você um dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:40.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{How very touching, obedient\Nsubordinate of mine. - OG}{How very touching,\Noh faithful subordinate of mine. - Gord}Que tocante,\Nó fiel subordinado meu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:45.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É isso que eu gosto em você, Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:51.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{A "New Era" is just around\Nthe corner. Do as you wish. - OG}Uma nova era está logo ali\Nna esquina. Faça o que quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:56.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But... I don't need you anymore. - OG}Porém... não preciso mais de você.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.13,0:19:11.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He took out the notorious Bellamy–\Na rookie worth 55 million– - OG}Ele acabou de derrubar um novato famoso\Nque valia 55 milhões!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:13.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{like he was a baby! - OG}Foi brincadeira de criança pra ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Finalmente está começando!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You'd better get ready! - OG}É melhor estarem preparados!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.30,0:19:23.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um mundo onde só piratas de verdade\Nsobrevivem está se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:25.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Those of you who are\Npowerless– run for your lives! - OG}Os fracos entre vocês—\Nfujam enquanto podem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Soon, the tide of the\Ntimes will wash over all - OG}Com as inevitáveis marés do tempo,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:31.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and a new era of\Nchampions will be upon us! - OG}uma nova era de campeões\Nem breve estará sobre nós!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
